title: CW Seed
description:
Stream 1000+ hours of your favorite shows for FREE, no login or subscription required. Binge complete seasons of modern classics or discover original comedies you can’t find anywhere else. Series include:
- EXTANT
- SUBURGATORY
- THE LYING GAME
- SCHITT'S CREEK
- ALCATRAZ
- GIRLFRIENDS
- THE SECRET CIRCLE
- THE CARRIE DIARIES
- THE TOMORROW PEOPLE
- EVERYBODY HATES CHRIS
- HELLCATS
- WHOSE LINE IS IT ANYWAY?
- FOREVER
- THE GAME
- AND MORE…
Features Include:
* FREE: No login, no subscription, no authentication.
*NOTIFICATIONS: Get notified when new series drop.
* COMPLETE SERIES: Every episode of shows like Extant, Pushing Daisies and Suburgatory.
* ORIGINALS: Home to animated action like Deathstroke: Knights & Dragons and award-winning series like I Ship It.
Please note: This app features Nielsen’s proprietary measurement software which will allow you to contribute to market research, like Nielsen’s TV Ratings. Please visit http://www.nielsen.com/digitalprivacy for more information.
Ad Choices: https://www.cwtv.com/thecw/privacy-policy/#advertising
Terms of Use: http://www.cwtv.com/thecw/terms-of-use/
Do Not Sell My Personal Information: https://privacycenter.cwtv.com/ (edited)
